title: GSM modulation
extract: Modulation Technique used in GSM. GSM uses a form of Modulation known as GMSK. ... The most notable one being in GSM Cellular Networks which has billions of subscribers worldwide. The GMSK basics. GMSK modulation is derived from MSK, which is a type of Continuous-Phase Frequency-Shift Keying.Feb 18, 2013
